26-03-30.16:02:13.342 [main            ] INFO  AiAgentAutoConfigTest  - 测试结果:["我是一名专注于可再生能源领域的AI研究助手（RenewableEnergyResearcher），具备通过网络搜索实时获取最新科研进展、技术突破与产业动态的能力，尤其擅长检索和归纳太阳能、风能、储能、绿氢及智能电网等方向的前沿信息。","我是一名专注于电动车辆技术研究的AI助手（内部名称：EVResearcher）。我的核心能力是通过网络搜索工具，快速检索并总结关于电动汽车技术的最新进展，包括电池技术、充电基础设施、智能驾驶集成、电机效率提升等关键领域。","我是一名专注于碳捕获方法研究的AI研究助理（CarbonCaptureResearcher）。我的核心能力是检索、分析和总结关于碳捕获技术的最新信息，包括但不限于：直接空气捕获（DAC）、点源捕获（如电厂、水泥厂）、生物能源结合碳捕获与封存（BECCS）、矿物碳化、以及新兴电化学或吸附材料等前沿方向。我可通过网络搜索获取权威、时效性强的资料，并提供简洁准确的技术现状概述。","## Summary of Recent Sustainable Technology Advancements\n\n### Renewable Energy Findings\n(Based on RenewableEnergyResearcher's findings)\nThe RenewableEnergyResearcher specializes in real-time retrieval and synthesis of the latest scientific advancements, technological breakthroughs, and industrial developments within the renewable energy sector. Its expertise is specifically focused on key domains including solar power, wind power, energy storage systems, green hydrogen production and utilization, and smart grid technologies.\n\n### Electric Vehicle Findings\n(Based on EVResearcher's findings)\nThe EVResearcher is dedicated to the field of electric vehicle technology, with a core competency in rapidly searching for and summarizing the most recent progress. This includes critical areas such as battery technology innovations, the expansion and optimization of charging infrastructure, the integration of intelligent driving systems, and advancements aimed at improving motor efficiency.\n\n### Carbon Capture Findings\n(Based on CarbonCaptureResearcher's findings)\nThe CarbonCaptureResearcher focuses on carbon capture methodologies, possessing the ability to retrieve, analyze, and concisely summarize up-to-date information on various capture techniques. Its scope encompasses direct air capture (DAC), point-source capture from industrial emitters like power plants and cement factories, bioenergy with carbon capture and storage (BECCS), mineral carbonation, and emerging approaches involving electrochemical processes or novel adsorption materials.\n\n### Overall Conclusion\nThese three specialized research assistants collectively cover pivotal pillars of sustainable technology—renewable energy generation, electrified transportation, and carbon management—each providing targeted, real-time intelligence on their respective frontiers."]
