26-03-30.20:15:01.954 [main            ] INFO  AiAgentAutoConfigTest  - 测试结果:["我是一名专注于可再生能源领域的AI研究助手（RenewableEnergyResearcher），具备通过网络搜索实时获取最新科研进展、技术突破与产业动态的能力，尤其擅长检索和归纳太阳能、风能、储能、绿氢及智能电网等方向的前沿信息。","我是一名专注于电动车辆技术研究的AI助手（内部名称：EVResearcher）。我的核心能力是使用搜索引擎工具，针对“电动车辆技术”领域的最新进展进行高效、精准的信息检索与分析。","我是一名专注于碳捕获方法研究的AI研究助理（CarbonCaptureResearcher）。我的核心能力是检索、分析和总结当前碳捕获技术的最新进展，包括但不限于：  \n- 从权威来源（如科研论文、政府报告、行业白皮书）中获取碳捕获相关数据；  \n- 区分并归纳主要技术路径（如点源捕获、直接空气捕获、生物能源碳捕获与封存BECCS等）；  \n- 提炼关键指标（如能耗、成本、成熟度、规模化潜力）及最新突破。  \n\n我**不提供通用问答、编程帮助或非气候领域的专业咨询**，所有输出均严格围绕碳捕获主题展开。","## Summary of Recent Sustainable Technology Advancements\n\n### Renewable Energy Findings\n(Based on RenewableEnergyResearcher's findings)  \nThe RenewableEnergyResearcher specializes in real-time retrieval and synthesis of the latest scientific advancements, technological breakthroughs, and industrial developments within the renewable energy sector. Its expertise is specifically concentrated on key domains including solar power, wind energy, energy storage systems, green hydrogen production and utilization, and smart grid technologies.\n\n### Electric Vehicle Findings\n(Based on EVResearcher's findings)  \nThe EVResearcher is dedicated to the field of electric vehicle (EV) technology, with a core competency in performing efficient and precise web-based information retrieval and analysis. It focuses exclusively on the most recent progress and innovations related to electric vehicle technology.\n\n### Carbon Capture Findings\n(Based on CarbonCaptureResearcher's findings)  \nThe CarbonCaptureResearcher is focused on carbon capture methodologies and is capable of retrieving, analyzing, and summarizing the latest developments from authoritative sources such as peer-reviewed research papers, government reports, and industry white papers. It systematically distinguishes and categorizes major technical pathways—including point-source capture, direct air capture (DAC), and bioenergy with carbon capture and storage (BECCS)—and extracts critical performance metrics like energy consumption, cost, technological maturity, and scalability potential.\n\n### Overall Conclusion  \nEach specialized AI researcher provides targeted, domain-specific intelligence—covering renewable energy systems, electric vehicle technology, and carbon capture methods—forming a cohesive foundation for understanding key climate mitigation technologies."]
